span.font: 1. The Balancer Server regularly collects the load information of each Worker Server with LM(load manager).

2. All App requests are sent directly to the Balancer Server, then the Balancer Server distributes the request to the appropriate Worker Server according to the load information and specific algorithms.
3. After the Worker Server processes the request done, it sends the response message back to the Balancer Server, and the Balancer Server continues to send the response to the original App.
